{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"animationend","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/animationend_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>animationend</code>&nbsp;事件会在一个 CSS 动画完成时触发（不包括完成前就已终止的情况，例如元素变得不可见或者动画从元素中移除）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常规信息","title":"常规信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"规范\">规范</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"CSS Animations Level 1\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"接口\">接口</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"是否冒泡\">是否冒泡</dt>\n <dd>是</dd>\n <dt id=\"事件可取消\">事件可取消</dt>\n <dd>否</dd>\n <dt id=\"目标\">目标</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"默认行为\">默认行为</dt>\n <dd>无</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性表","title":"属性表","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">属性</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">类型</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件目标（DOM 顶层目标）。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件类型</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n   <td>事件是否正常冒泡？</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n   <td>可否取消该事件？</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>animationName</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>与该动画相关的 CSS 属性值。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>elapsedTime</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><code>Float</code></td>\n   <td>动画运行时长，单位为秒，与直到该事件被触发的时间相一致，不包括任何动画暂停时的时长。应等于 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/animation-iteration-count\"><code>animation-iteration-count</code></a> 乘以 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/animation-duration\"><code>animation-duration</code></a> 的积，动画总活动的时长。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"{{Specifications}}"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/animationstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">animationstart (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/animationiteration_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">animationiteration (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/animationcancel\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">animationcancel</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations\">CSS Animations</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations